Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:04.38,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:18.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:19.56,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The Pope...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.11,CRZero,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,His Holiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.01,CRZero,Knight2,0000,0000,0000,,W-Was eaten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:36.56,CRZero,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,R-Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:38.08,CRZero,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,All men retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito? Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:50.80,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got to hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:53.03,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.96,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Louise's Choice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.70,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So long, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:41.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Derf...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Derf!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:45.92,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.44,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,-Saito!\N-Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:53.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the Versailles Palace in Lutèce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:54.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:57.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,In Lutèce?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:00.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what about the Ancient Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:01.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.10,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:10.13,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.94,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it suddenly stopped after passing \Nthrough the valley of Oltia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.69,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:19.73,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,That huge thing curled up \Nand solidified like a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.65,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:29.39,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,of His Holiness defeated the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.42,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.20,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Its heart continues to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.25,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I do not believe it is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.24,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it will soon rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.39,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.44,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:52.15,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,You answered my call, Old Osmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.15,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.41,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to His \NHoliness is a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.35,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.48,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.12,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Right now though, I'm focused \Non the Ancient Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.48,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that's what His Holiness \Nwould wish for as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.28,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:17.17,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you summoned me because \Nof this Ancient Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.06,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Old Osmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:24.08,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell us about the research \Nyou did along with your work at
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.91,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,the Academy of Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:30.72,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:33.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess we'll just have \Nto get him good next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.06,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to avenge the Pope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:42.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Louise? Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.20,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.09,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta, do we have anything to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.91,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll go heat up \Nsome soup right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.93,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Where are all the people \Nfrom the academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.71,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they went back to Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.65,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Lukshana and her friend said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.81,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,that they're returning to your mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.95,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,so they're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.42,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.79,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a while before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,we can go back there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:17.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to go help Siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.47,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.34,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.71,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't watch anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito didn't say a single \Nthing about Derf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But I know he's really sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:42.45,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably because \NSaito's so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.85,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,and trying his best to—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.63,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have to be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:47.94,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.71,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted him to say that he could \Nno longer fight without Derf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.97,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted him to say he wouldn't use \Nthe power of Lífþrasir anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.60,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not blaming you, Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:03.53,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to watch Saito \Nwhittle away his life any further...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.54,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.05,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,And that is all I have learned
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:16.35,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,about the Ancient Dragon \Nthrough my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:19.82,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Louise and Tiffania
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:23.01,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,have even harder trials to get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:29.03,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,I will speak more to \Nthose two about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.91,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the mistake was to face
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.78,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,the dragon without the Four \Nand Four being reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.55,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that in the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.35,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,the dragon in the past was defeated by
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.01,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,the Four and Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:45.35,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,However, it does not say that \Nnobody else can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:53.17,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Our culture has advanced much \Nin the last 6,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:57.31,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Today, there are bonds in Halkeginia \Nthat transcend borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:01.51,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,It is perhaps possible that \Nthat's enough to cover
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.87,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,for the incomplete Four and Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:12.26,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Charlotte, Tristain will raise \Nall of her military resources
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.46,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,to beat back this crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:17.12,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Will Gallia join us in this fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.65,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:23.54,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Let us ask for the \Ncooperation of Romalia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.23,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,and the other countries as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.80,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect the future of Halkeginia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.33,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,with our own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,All the countries of \NHalkeginia have formed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.01,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,an alliance to fight the Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:46.79,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I was chosen to lead the alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.54,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to fight \Nthe Ancient Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,the Void Mages are needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:55.66,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, we were all born in Halkeginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.81,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,We were all nurtured by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.86,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stand by
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.93,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,and do nothing when our \Nworld is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.44,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,If it raises the chances of defeating \Nthe dragon even a tiny bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.40,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,we will join the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.88,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:18.03,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I will also fight with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.23,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who was born in Halkeginia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:23.04,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I will offer myself completely to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.32,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:27.90,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's overcome this crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.09,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Come what may!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.04,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As someone who was born in Halkeginia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will offer myself completely to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:45.97,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was born here, so that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.97,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.88,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito wasn't born in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can we actually involve him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.92,CRZero,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:05.79,CRZero,Soldier2,0000,0000,0000,,We'll defeat the dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:06.98,CRZero,Soldier3,0000,0000,0000,,Have no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.40,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.20,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Derf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:22.23,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The machine sunk in the oasis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.22,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that iron cylinder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:25.69,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to use that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.68,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,No, that one was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.16,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wondering if there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.35,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,weren't more like it in the elven lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:34.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Locked away somewhere and kept safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:35.97,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.44,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I haven't heard \Nof anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,There goes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.33,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth a shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,If we had a fighter plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.19,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,we could take that Ancient \NDragon down in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.07,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,So they're called "fighter planes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:52.20,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.33,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's a weapon from my world that can \Nfly through the sky really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,And its missiles can \Neven sink a battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:09:59.98,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Missiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.50,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,If that's such a great weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.90,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,then why don't you go back to your world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.29,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,and bring one back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.30,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.74,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not use Louise's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.43,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the World Door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:16.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Would that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.97,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason why \Nthat wouldn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But my world is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:23.57,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.51,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to connect the World \NDoor to Saito's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:35.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If it works, let's go get that fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:36.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.05,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.00,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's verify the procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.78,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,First, Louise will open a \Nwindow to Saito's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.58,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Using Saito's powers, she'll enlarge \Nit so they can pass through it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.26,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he telling them what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.40,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,He likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.38,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.58,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've got the fighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.01,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,you'll use Louise's power \Nagain to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.01,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:17.13,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think we can \Nget back to my world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.29,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.43,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We should get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.04,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use a little of your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:33.84,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:37.04,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Send me an image of your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:44.52,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Ken Gyof Hagaras Soir Beok Daeg...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:48.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, door to Saito's \Nworld, please open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.66,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Those buildings look so weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.68,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,This is your world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, it's my world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:23.03,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.05,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.23,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:40.04,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I really loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:43.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting you made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.34,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So please remember
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.94,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,that the last thing you saw me do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,was smile at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:55.49,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:58.92,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:08.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:11.53,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.63,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.74,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:18.36,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,We need him to defeat the Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:22.50,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito came from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:26.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to get him tangled \Nup in the fate of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:30.02,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is a Void Mage's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.19,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:31.97,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Ari...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.88,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.17,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:46.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:56.80,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louise truly loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:01.23,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she didn't, she could have \Nnever made this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:11.40,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.77,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.07,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.57,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:21.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:25.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I returned him to the \Nworld where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:31.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, but I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:41.39,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I would have \Ndone the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.15,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.85,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.53,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:50.09,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:54.87,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to you that I will defeat \Nthe dragon with my own power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:59.04,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,without the need to borrow \Nthe power of Lífþrasir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:05.52,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also bet everything \NI have on this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:09.39,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.46,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.01,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,To the Academy of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.44,CRZero,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:36.07,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that once upon a time, \Nthe Ancient Dragon was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.49,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,sealed away by the Void Mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.50,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,However, according to the texts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.89,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Void Mages also enhance the \NAncient Dragon's powers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.11,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,if they are eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.23,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon gets stronger \Nby consuming the Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:56.82,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why he instinctively \Nseeks out places with Void Mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:16:00.18,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,So the reason the dragon first \Nturned towards Romalia was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.94,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,He sensed the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:06.01,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,of a Void Mage, the Pope, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:10.25,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,And once he wakes again, \Nhe will target...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.87,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Me, or Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:17.46,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why we're taking you \Nto the Academy of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.77,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,There are no settlements around there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:24.22,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no worry of collateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:29.53,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, the military is set \Nup along the estimated route
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:33.80,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,of the dragon and will attack \Nhim with all their might.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.97,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know if it will have any effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.04,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:41.51,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But if we fight at the Academy, \Nthe students will all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.91,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:46.18,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Colbert is evacuating everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.97,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta! I told you to return to the mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,with Lukshana and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.97,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,But we're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:58.56,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her to bring us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.17,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to see \Nthe Academy of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.91,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.50,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already been evacuated, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.41,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Louise, Tiffania!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:16.05,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,You're later than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.25,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I was just telling everybody \Nabout the formation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.05,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with for defeating the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:23.14,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.63,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.39,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha, weren't you just at the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:32.86,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,I flew at max speed and overtook you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:36.27,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, Old Osmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.57,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody insisted on staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:42.87,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.77,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay here, you might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.16,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think we could just ignore this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:54.31,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,We also want to protect the \Nworld that we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:18:00.84,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,It is our duty as the Undine Order \Nto protect you in Saito's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.29,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.16,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, doesn't this kind of \Nthing make your heart race?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.09,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Jeanette! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.26,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I hired them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:17.14,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,They're mercenaries. \NThey'll fight for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.05,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.22,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad to have us as allies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:27.13,CRZero,Damien,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we want this \Nworld to get destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:30.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.47,CRZero,Damien,0000,0000,0000,,Will you two lend a hand, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:36.02,CRZero,Damien,0000,0000,0000,,Having another user of indigenous magic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.93,CRZero,Damien,0000,0000,0000,,would really make things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.59,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.38,CRZero,Damien,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. That's really helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:43.48,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lukshana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:48.81,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it would benefit Nephthys \Nto get rid of the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.64,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,How about a late night snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.50,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:08.83,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's because I made \Nsuch a pathetic face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why Louise did \Nthis to prevent me from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:13.77,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}using the power of Lífþrasir again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But without this power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:19.19,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Ancient Dragon can't be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.71,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.72,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louise will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe... Maybe over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:31.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:35.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That day, the Gate of \NLight opened here and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I was summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise? Can't you hear me, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! Hey, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:49.23,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.34,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:55.65,CRZero,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,"Louise! Louise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.81,CRZero,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get dumped by \Nyour favorite maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.05,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.65,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don't tell me you're crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.02,CRZero,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.02,CRZero,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you got dumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.21,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:22.71,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Showed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.54,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all for nothing, \Nthis loser's broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:25.55,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:34.05,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't get back to \NHalkeginia by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:37.38,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:39.80,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.22,CRZero,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:54.03,CRZero,Knight2,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:55.55,CRZero,Knight3,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.50,CRZero,Knight4,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.61,CRZero,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get back! Everyone back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:12.84,CRZero,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.26,CRZero,Officer,0000,0000,0000,,Something is approaching from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.82,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,From the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.50,CRZero,Officer,0000,0000,0000,,That's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:29.43,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Ancient Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.38,CRZero,Officer,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know it could fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:32.94,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Attack right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:29.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're not here anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.34,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure you're \Nliving on in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:32.66,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,where you're supposed be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:34.59,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.59,0:23:37.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, tune in for the last \Nepisode, "Zero's Familiar."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:41.00,Next-Ep-Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(290,1)}Zero's Familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:40.38,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything, Saito!
